{"id":2915,"date":"2019-09-13T07:44:51","date_gmt":"2019-09-13T07:44:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=2915"},"modified":"2019-12-31T11:26:40","modified_gmt":"2019-12-31T04:26:40","slug":"loi-khuyen-thiet-ke-website","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-khuyen-thiet-ke-website.html\/","title":{"rendered":"5 L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-khuyen-thiet-ke-website.html\/#Xac_chu_de_cua_website\" title=\"X\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a website\">X\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a website<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-khuyen-thiet-ke-website.html\/#Xac_dinh_cau_truc_website\" title=\"X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac website\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac website<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-khuyen-thiet-ke-website.html\/#Noi_dung_trang_web_thong_nhat\" title=\"N\u1ed9i dung trang web th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t\">N\u1ed9i dung trang web th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-khuyen-thiet-ke-website.html\/#Toc_do_tai_trang_nhanh\" title=\"T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea3i trang nhanh\">T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea3i trang nhanh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-khuyen-thiet-ke-website.html\/#Lam_so_do_trang_web_site_map\" title=\"L\u00e0m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 trang web (site map)\">L\u00e0m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 trang web (site map)<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em>S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng truy c\u1eadp s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu trang web doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy c\u1eadp d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y trong v\u00f4 v\u00e0n nh\u1eefng trang web tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng. Mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trang web c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1eeb 1 \u2013 30 tr\u00ean Google \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1eeb kho\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y cung c\u1ea5p cho b\u1ea1n 5<strong> l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, <\/strong>v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm khi <strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website<\/strong>\u00a0c\u00f4ng ty,\u00a0<strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf web\u00a0doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong>.<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Xac_chu_de_cua_website\"><\/span><strong>X\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a website<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Meta Tags ( th\u1ebb si\u00eau d\u1eef li\u1ec7u ) bao g\u1ed3m 3 lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 , t\u1eeb kho\u00e1 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 trang web. Ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong 3 lo\u1ea1i meta tags. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap thu h\u00fat t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 truy c\u1eadp th\u00f4ng qua k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm v\u1edbi t\u1eeb kho\u00e1 hay nh\u00f3m t\u1eeb th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n<p>N\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 bao g\u1ed3m t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb cho trang web c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Meta tags n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed9i dung trang web v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong ph\u1ea7n n\u00f4i dung.<\/p>\n<p>S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a trong m\u1ed9t trang web kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean qu\u00e1 3 l\u1ea7n , v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u00ec hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n . Meta Tags m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1i tag n\u00e0y v\u00e0 n\u00f3 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 n\u1ed9i dung website gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy c\u1eadp d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a trang web ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ViEtDeVdIvId\">\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Xac_dinh_cau_truc_website\"><\/span><strong>X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac website<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u00e1c h\u1ecda s\u01a1 qua n\u1ed9i dung c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a trang web. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh trang web c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c ra sao. V\u00ed d\u1ee5, m\u1ed9t trang web v\u1ec1 s\u00e1ch kinh t\u1ebf, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ri\u00eang cho nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i s\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0 : ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb, qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb, t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh k\u1ebf to\u00e1n, lu\u1eadt, xu\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u v.v\u2026 Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n l\u1ea1i ngh\u1ec9 t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c con, nh\u01b0 trong s\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb c\u00f3<a href=\"https:\/\/wikimarketing.vn\/mot-so-khai-niem-marketing.html\/\"> ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/a>, ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikimarketing.vn\/nghien-cuu-thi-truong-la-gi-dinh-nghia.html\/\">nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/a>, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o , ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u2026<\/p>\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cau-truc-silo-cho-website.html\/\">C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac silo x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng website<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2886\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2886\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2886 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u00e1c-lo\u1ea1i-c\u1ea5u-tr\u00fac-silo-trong-seo.jpg\" alt=\"c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac web trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website \" width=\"825\" height=\"460\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u00e1c-lo\u1ea1i-c\u1ea5u-tr\u00fac-silo-trong-seo.jpg 825w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u00e1c-lo\u1ea1i-c\u1ea5u-tr\u00fac-silo-trong-seo-300x167.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u00e1c-lo\u1ea1i-c\u1ea5u-tr\u00fac-silo-trong-seo-768x428.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2886\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xong ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 cho website ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Noi_dung_trang_web_thong_nhat\"><\/span><strong>N\u1ed9i dung trang web th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. C\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3 thi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c nhau , th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh sao cho h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. \u0110\u1ec3 trang web n\u1eb1m \u1edf top 10 trong k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm , b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u0129 c\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t.<\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 hai ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u00ean: n\u1ed9i dung ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0 n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2827\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2827\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2827\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ed1-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-ch\u1eef-trong-b\u00e0i-vi\u1ebft-\u0111\u00f3ng-m\u1ed9t-vai-tr\u00f2-quan-tr\u1ecdng-ch\u1ea5m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.jpg\" alt=\"l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website\" width=\"825\" height=\"543\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ed1-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-ch\u1eef-trong-b\u00e0i-vi\u1ebft-\u0111\u00f3ng-m\u1ed9t-vai-tr\u00f2-quan-tr\u1ecdng-ch\u1ea5m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ed1-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-ch\u1eef-trong-b\u00e0i-vi\u1ebft-\u0111\u00f3ng-m\u1ed9t-vai-tr\u00f2-quan-tr\u1ecdng-ch\u1ea5m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-300x198.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ed1-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-ch\u1eef-trong-b\u00e0i-vi\u1ebft-\u0111\u00f3ng-m\u1ed9t-vai-tr\u00f2-quan-tr\u1ecdng-ch\u1ea5m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-768x506.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/s\u1ed1-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-ch\u1eef-trong-b\u00e0i-vi\u1ebft-\u0111\u00f3ng-m\u1ed9t-vai-tr\u00f2-quan-tr\u1ecdng-ch\u1ea5m-\u0111i\u1ec3m-ch\u1ea5t-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-1024x674.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2827\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">N\u1ed9i dung b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 doanh nghi\u1ec7p cung c\u1ea5p c\u1ea7n xoanh quanh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 d\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Toc_do_tai_trang_nhanh\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea3i trang nhanh<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm, c\u00e1c trang link t\u1eeb trang ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 350 \u0111\u1ebfn 550 t\u1eeb. Khi n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trang qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean chia th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u trang kh\u00e1c nhau , tuy v\u1eady n\u00ean gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean c\u00e1ch tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y (layout) ban \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng trang v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 100 Kb. V\u00ec th\u1ebf b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a trang web.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2917\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2917\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2917\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u1ea7n-c\u1ea3i-thi\u1ec7n-web-speed-nhi\u1ec1u-nh\u1ea5t-c\u00f3-th\u1ec3.jpg\" alt=\"l\u01b0u \u00fd khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website \" width=\"825\" height=\"471\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u1ea7n-c\u1ea3i-thi\u1ec7n-web-speed-nhi\u1ec1u-nh\u1ea5t-c\u00f3-th\u1ec3.jpg 1680w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u1ea7n-c\u1ea3i-thi\u1ec7n-web-speed-nhi\u1ec1u-nh\u1ea5t-c\u00f3-th\u1ec3-300x171.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u1ea7n-c\u1ea3i-thi\u1ec7n-web-speed-nhi\u1ec1u-nh\u1ea5t-c\u00f3-th\u1ec3-768x439.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/c\u1ea7n-c\u1ea3i-thi\u1ec7n-web-speed-nhi\u1ec1u-nh\u1ea5t-c\u00f3-th\u1ec3-1024x585.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2917\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n web speed nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Lam_so_do_trang_web_site_map\"><\/span><strong>L\u00e0m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 trang web (site map)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 trang web s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch cho c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy c\u1eadp l\u1eabn c\u00e1c con nh\u1ec7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm. C\u00e1ch s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng li\u00ean k\u1ebft HTML bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 (v\u00ed d\u1ee5 thay v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a \u201cqu\u1ea7n \u00e1o\u201d m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chung chung n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0 \u201cqu\u1ea7n \u00e1o tr\u1ebb em\u201d). S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 trang web n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ed1i k\u1ebft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 trang web.<\/p>\n<p><em>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb l\u01b0u \u00fd v\u00e0 <strong>l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website<\/strong>. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-website-wordpress.html\/\">d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website wordpress c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng truy c\u1eadp s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu trang web doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy c\u1eadp d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y trong v\u00f4 v\u00e0n nh\u1eefng trang web tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng. Mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trang web c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1eeb 1 \u2013 30 tr\u00ean Google \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1eeb&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2918,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[51,55],"tags":[114],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>5 L\u1